('Husk Cherry', 'Goldie is tasty heirloom husk cherry! This husk cherry ripens to a lovely orange and is best enjoyed in pies. Goldie is known for its very sweet flavor that does well in different types of jams and jellies. This low growing, very prolific vine husk cherry is a favorite!', 1.5, 3.00,'sun','https://www.ufseeds.com/dw/image/v2/BFKV_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-master-urbanfarmer/default/dw42c914b8/images/products/Ground-Cherry-Tomato-Seeds.jpg?sw=275&sh=275', '3,4,5,6,7,8,9'),
